# C2 Beacon — Campaign ID in URI
alert http $HOME_NET any -> $EXTERNAL_NET any (msg:"ORDERBUDDY C2 Beacon - Campaign ID 40abc1fa2901"; flow:to_server,established; http.uri; content:"/s/40abc1fa2901"; classtype:trojan-activity; sid:2026001; rev:1; metadata:created_at 2026_02_28, updated_at 2026_02_28;)

